data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with full basement on a cul-de-sac. This home has been completely updated. New kitchen, flooring, baths, fixtures, paint, hot water tank, dehumidifier, and beautiful landscaping. New roof, exterior doors and windows. Partially finished basement with plenty of room for storage.
